<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4631435>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Clubiona apiculata sp. nov.; male holotype (A–E); female paratype (F,G). Male palp; (A) ventral view, (B) prolateral view, (C) retrolateral view, (D) dorsal view. (E) Apex of tegulum showing conductor, prolateral view. (F) Epigyne, ventral view. (G) Internal genitalia, dorsal view. Scale bars: A–D, 0.1 mm; F,G, 0.25 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4631435/files/figure.png" .

